Package: r.oguelike
Title: Play a Roguelike Game In The Console
Version: 0.0.0.9006
Authors@R:
    person("Matt", "Dray", , "mwdray@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Play a simple ASCII-only tile-based game in the console inspired 
    heavily by roguelike games, particularly Rogue (1980) itself. Work in 
    progress.
